parameters:
\FF[himawari_shadow]Himawari: "Stop doing weird things! It's pointless to do
this to me!!"

\FF[himawari_shadow]Himawari: "Because... I am!... Eh...? Who am I...?
Eh...eh...?"

\FF[himawari_shadow]Himawari: "Who was it again? No, it doesn't matter who...
Fuuuh I'm starting not to care anymore"

\FF[himawari_shadow]Himawari: "Anyone will do If it feels good, that's all that
matters..."

\FF[himawari_free]Himawari: "Sora and the Iris Blade and all that... I was
silly to be so fixated on them!"

\FF[himawari_free]Himawari: "Aahh~! What a waste of time I've lost out in
life~ From now on, I'll be a fool who thinks of nothing~"

\FF[kikyou_shadow]Kikyo: "Gah! To attack without touching... That's so
underhanded..!!"

\FF[kikyou_shadow]Kikyo: "You must think it's too late for me! How naive! Do
you have any idea how many perverted monsters I've fought?!"

\FF[kikyou_shadow]Kikyo: "With the experience of Seiryu Kikyo, I can resist
such brainwashing powers!! ...wait, Kikyo?"

\FF[kikyou_shadow]Kikyo: "Umm... who's there...? Eheehee... My sensitivity is
increasing"

\FF[kikyou_shadow]Kikyo: "I can't remember but... it doesn't matter anymore I
can't... ahhhh beat this pleasure"

\FF[kikyou_shadow]Kikyo: "I'm such a weakling to pleasure, a pathetic female
Ahhhn It feels so good..."

\FF[kikyou_free]Kikyo: "Kufuu... It's good to be weak... If I were too
strong... I wouldn't be able to experience this wonderful
feeling of release"

\FF[kikyou_free]Kikyo: "Master, I will follow you for life Anywhere and
with anyone... I want to make love"

\F[iruka_trouble]Iruka: "This world has become so different, it's like no
simulation could have prepared us... Where are we...?"

\F[iruka_trouble]Iruka: "To suddenly have Akane Suzaku appear right in front
of me... It almost seems possible."

\FF[himawari_trouble]Himawari: "Suzukake Senpai, you're safe. Do you know what
happened to everyone? I got separated from Sora..."

\FF[himawari_angry]Himawari: "You said that when it's time to do it, you have
to take everything off... That was you, Kikyo, right?"

\FF[kikyou_trouble]Kikyo: "Th-that's true, but... that was because I was
brainwashed by Poison..."
\F[iruka_trouble]\FF[kikyou_trouble]\AA[1]Iruka: "Oh, are you two... agents as well?"
\F[iruka_trouble]\FF[himawari_trouble]\AA[2]Himawari: "No, that's not it. We're just ordinary people!"
\F[iruka_trouble]\FF[kikyou_trouble]\AA[2]Kikyo: "Ordinary people is... not quite right either..."

\F[furi_smile]Akane: "Senpai~! I found you What is everyone doing? Please
let me join in too~"

\F[furi_smile]Akane: "No, maybe it's you seniors who will be joining us
Hehehe There's no escape now!"

\FF[iruka_erod]Iruka: "Ah, I know why you joined the detective club, Akane
Suzaku-san. It was to catch the criminal who attacked
Shiratora-san in the past, right...?"

\FF[iruka_erod]Iruka: "It's not just a game... I... that's why I support
you... but... but still... ahhhh..."

\FF[iruka_erod]Iruka: "Support...? Who needs it...? I don't need anything
like that..."

\FF[iruka_erod]Iruka: "You should just do as you please Ahaha That's
right... There's no need for a reason If it feels good,
that's all that matters"

\FF[iruka_free]Iruka: "Motives, whether it's intentional or accidental,
really it doesn't matter Detectives are the ones who fuss
over the most trivial things, aren't they"

\F[furi_smile]\FF[iruka_free]\AA[1]Akane: "Yeah. It doesn't matter what happened at the
beginning. It's fine even without any basis or evidence."

\F[furi_smile]\FF[iruka_free]\AA[1]Akane: "We've been freed from all those entanglements.
Just... if 'now' feels good, that's enough"

\F[furi_smile]\FF[iruka_free]\AA[2]Iruka: "That's right I understand We have to teach
Shiratora-san who is stuck in the worthless past..."

\F[furi_smile]\FF[iruka_free]\AA[1]Akane: "Yes... That's it! We'll free Nadeshiko from her
past How wonderful"
